  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a imlib2</title>

    <para>
      <application>imlib2</application> is a graphics library for fast file
loading, saving, rendering and manipulation.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Informação do Pacote</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Transferência (HTTP): <ulink url="&imlib2-download-http;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Transferência (FTP): <ulink url="&imlib2-download-ftp;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Soma de verificação MD5: &imlib2-md5sum;
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Tamanho da transferência: &imlib2-size;
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Espaço em disco estimado exigido: &imlib2-buildsize;
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Tempo de construção estimado: &imlib2-time;
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Dependências de imlib2</bridgehead>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Exigida</bridgehead>
    <para role="required">
      <xref linkend="xorg7-lib"/>
    </para>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Recomendada</bridgehead>
    <para role="recommended">
      <xref linkend="giflib"/>
    </para>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Opcionais</bridgehead>
    <para role="optional">
      <xref linkend="doxygen"/> (for API documentation), <xref linkend="libpng"/>,
<xref linkend="libjpeg"/>, <xref linkend="libtiff"/>, <xref
linkend="x265"/>, and <ulink
url="https://sourceforge.net/projects/mad">libid3tag</ulink>
    </para>

    <para condition="html" role="usernotes">Observações de Usuário(a): <ulink url="&blfs-wiki;/imlib2"/></para>

  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Instalação de imlib2</title>

    <para>
      Instale <application>imlib2</application> executando os seguintes comandos:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr --disable-static &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Esse pacote não vem com uma suíte de teste.
    </para>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usuário(a) &root;:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      If you generated the API documentation, install it as the &root; user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>install -v -m755 -d            /usr/share/doc/imlib2-&imlib2-version;/html &amp;&amp;
install -v -m644    doc/html/* /usr/share/doc/imlib2-&imlib2-version;/html</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

